# Input

```yml
.anchors:
  - &anchor1
    key: value
  - &anchor2
    another: prop

foo:
  bar: baz
  <<: *anchor1
  <<: *anchor2

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -7,4 +7,4 @@
 foo:
   bar: baz
   <<: *anchor1
-  <<: *anchor2
+  <<: *anchor2
\ No newline at end of file
```

# Output

```yml
.anchors:
  - &anchor1
    key: value
  - &anchor2
    another: prop

foo:
  bar: baz
  <<: *anchor1
  <<: *anchor2```

